1
00:00:00,180 --> 00:00:03,240
The Cage of Love

2
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:12,430
<i>Episode 17</i>

3
00:00:28,530 --> 00:00:30,600
Wu Cai Hong.

4
00:00:42,480 --> 00:00:44,870
Are you okay? Let me take a look.

5
00:00:44,870 --> 00:00:46,830
I'm fine.

6
00:00:46,830 --> 00:00:49,010
- Let me do it.
- Don't tidy up.

7
00:00:49,010 --> 00:00:52,100
Come here, quick.

8
00:00:57,800 --> 00:01:00,080
Does it hurt?

9
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:01,520
Is it painful?

10
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,690
I'm fine.

11
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:15,680
You are still thinking about Zhou Shao Tian.

12
00:01:19,070 --> 00:01:23,890
I don't know what his place in my heart is.

13
00:01:26,130 --> 00:01:29,510
I remember when my father was alive,

14
00:01:29,510 --> 00:01:31,680
our home was filled with visitors.

15
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:36,650
My father would always praise Brother Shao Tian,

16
00:01:36,650 --> 00:01:43,180
but in my heart, he was just a good friend and like a brother.

17
00:01:43,180 --> 00:01:48,180
When my father passed away, all my relatives and friends

18
00:01:48,180 --> 00:01:50,880
pretended not to know me.

19
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:54,120
They ignored me too.

20
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:58,520
I only had Brother Shao Tian. No matter who abandoned us,

21
00:01:58,520 --> 00:02:03,500
he would think of ways to help us.

22
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:07,970
At that time, I really didn't know what to do.

23
00:02:07,970 --> 00:02:10,640
During that period of time,

24
00:02:10,640 --> 00:02:15,620
if it wasn't for Brother Shao Tian, I don't know how we would have gotten through.

25
00:02:17,330 --> 00:02:22,330
If Brother Shao Tian took the money from Ling Long

26
00:02:22,330 --> 00:02:27,820
and killed my father, then, in this world,

27
00:02:27,820 --> 00:02:32,960
I really don't know who to trust.

28
00:02:35,550 --> 00:02:41,100
Sometimes, you need to face the truth.

29
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:51,980
By the way, why are you looking for me?

30
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:59,770
Have you ever seen Zhou Shao Tian's Parker fountain pen?

31
00:02:59,770 --> 00:03:04,970
Why would Brother Shao Tian have a Parker fountain pen? What do you mean?

32
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:08,590
Never mind.

33
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:18,950
Mr Jiang. This is the oversea's address of the fountain pen that you wanted.

34
00:03:18,950 --> 00:03:20,320
Thanks.

35
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:27,460
Don't mention it, Mr Jiang. If you need anything, please let us know. Our shop can also order goods for you.

36
00:03:27,460 --> 00:03:29,220
No need for the time being.

37
00:03:29,220 --> 00:03:32,560
Fei Fei, please see Boss Fu out.

38
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,840
- Okay.
- Mr Jiang, I'm taking my leave first.

39
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,920
Bye.

40
00:03:50,050 --> 00:03:51,630
- Hello.
- I would like to trouble you.

41
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:54,130
Please send a telegram to this address.

42
00:03:54,130 --> 00:03:56,030
Okay.

43
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,170
What is the message of the telegram?

44
00:03:59,170 --> 00:04:01,360
Please keep it short.

45
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:04,530
Dear Sir or Madam. How are you?

46
00:04:04,530 --> 00:04:07,300
I previously purchased a Parker fountain pen from you.

47
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:13,450
There is a problem with it now. May I ask if I can use the warranty for repairs?

48
00:04:13,450 --> 00:04:15,430
- Is that all?
- Yes.

49
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:18,000
Okay. Your name, please.

50
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:22,630
Zhou Shao Tian.

51
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:24,950
Zhou Shao Tian.

52
00:04:51,230 --> 00:04:54,920
Why are you day dreaming in front of me instead of working?

53
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:57,490
I would like to take some time off to go out for a while.

54
00:04:57,490 --> 00:04:59,550
Take time off?

55
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:05,390
Why are you taking time off when my brother has gone out?

56
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:09,270
Are you going for a rendezvous and are afraid that my brother will find out?

57
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:12,550
I will be back soon.

58
00:05:12,550 --> 00:05:15,770
I hope that you never come back ever.

59
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:20,430
I will be back soon.

60
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:24,440
Okay, go.

61
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:26,990
I will take it as I didn't see this

62
00:05:26,990 --> 00:05:29,930
but if my brother were to find out,

63
00:05:29,930 --> 00:05:33,990
and he beats or scolds you, it's your problem then.

64
00:05:33,990 --> 00:05:35,860
Thank you.

65
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:47,050
Hello, Miss Lu.

66
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:50,910
Miss Wu. What brings you here?

67
00:05:50,910 --> 00:05:54,180
It's such a surprise. Come, take a seat.

68
00:05:54,180 --> 00:05:55,630
No need.

69
00:05:55,630 --> 00:06:02,190
I would like to ask you if Brother Shao Tian borrowed $500,000 from you.

70
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:04,120
Regarding this matter,

71
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,740
yes, he did.

72
00:06:05,740 --> 00:06:09,910
He said that he used his life in exchange for it. Is this true?

73
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:15,150
How could you use someone's life in exchange?

74
00:06:15,150 --> 00:06:21,770
I'm a business woman. There is nothing that can't be traded with business transactions.

75
00:06:21,770 --> 00:06:25,230
What are you going to use Brother Shao Tian's life for?

76
00:06:25,230 --> 00:06:31,280
I don't want Zhou Shao Tian's life but you should know that there is chaos in the military now.

77
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:34,090
There will always be someone who would trade his life for a task.

78
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:38,700
Where is he? I want to see him. We will return the money to you.

79
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,800
I'm afraid it's already too late.

80
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:44,760
He should already be on the way there.

81
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:47,650
Are you joking with me now?

82
00:06:47,650 --> 00:06:50,530
What did you task him with?

83
00:06:50,530 --> 00:06:54,300
Miss Wu. I think you already read the newspapers.

84
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:57,540
The Yao Jiangsu and Zhejiang War has already broken out. <i>War between two providences.</i>

85
00:06:57,540 --> 00:07:00,010
The army and Shanghai's army are allies.

86
00:07:00,010 --> 00:07:04,310
Shao Tian is taking cloth on through to the frontline

87
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:06,620
to give to the General in Shanghai.

88
00:07:06,620 --> 00:07:08,970
Why did you send him there?

89
00:07:08,970 --> 00:07:14,240
It's because this is a very important mission. He must not make a mistake. If he doesn't do it well,

90
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:18,310
Mr Zhou is an important part of the business.

91
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:24,310
Of course, a smart person will not go but there is no one as brave as Zhou Shao Tian.

92
00:07:24,310 --> 00:07:29,810
Zhou Shao Tian is the most suitable person that I know.

93
00:07:29,810 --> 00:07:33,600
Especially, when he needed a big sum of money to buy the house.

94
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:38,570
Who are you to him? It is like you forced him to go.

95
00:07:38,570 --> 00:07:42,920
I really didn't force him. He went willingly.

96
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:46,250
He really wanted to buy the house back for you.

97
00:07:46,250 --> 00:07:50,980
Instead you should thank me for helping him fulfill his wish.

98
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:53,080
I don't need the house.

99
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:56,130
I don't need him to risk his life either.

100
00:07:56,130 --> 00:08:02,300
It's already too late now. The plan is at 12 noon. He should have already left.

101
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:06,340
Even if Zhou Shao Tian didn't tell you that he's going to the frontline,

102
00:08:11,730 --> 00:08:14,340
it looks like he really loves you very much.

103
00:08:15,260 --> 00:08:18,010
He only doesn't want you to worry.

104
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:25,940
Frankly, I did ask him why he wanted to buy the house.

105
00:08:25,940 --> 00:08:29,930
He said that it was not just a house.

106
00:08:29,930 --> 00:08:35,540
It contains all your childhood memories. It contains the memories of your mother and her garden.

107
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:42,360
Also, when he was nineteen years old,

108
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:45,110
he saw you for the first time. You were reading a book.

109
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:56,070
<i>It's a pity that there aren't any men in this world who can help me to find my memories that I lost.</i>

110
00:08:56,070 --> 00:08:59,990
<i>Otherwise, I wouldn't have come to this point.</i>

111
00:09:10,370 --> 00:09:12,110
Stepmom!

112
00:09:12,110 --> 00:09:14,030
Stepmom!

113
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:16,960
Stepmom!

114
00:09:18,130 --> 00:09:19,150
Stepmom!

115
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:20,870
Coming.

116
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:22,710
Stepmom!

117
00:09:22,710 --> 00:09:25,090
What's going on? Why are you so anxious? Look at her.

118
00:09:25,090 --> 00:09:27,400
Is Brother Shao Tian still here?

119
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:31,740
He left after he brought Cai Yun here.

120
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:33,560
Why would he be here?

121
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:36,270
Aren't he and his mother staying here?

122
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:38,620
Isn't he living with his mother at his house?

123
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:41,730
Why would he be living here?

124
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:45,890
Cai Hong. You just came back. Why are you leaving so soon?

125
00:09:50,250 --> 00:09:51,740
Brother Shao Tian.

126
00:09:51,740 --> 00:09:53,840
Coming.

127
00:09:56,230 --> 00:09:58,260
- Aunt.
- Miss Wu, what brings you here?

128
00:09:58,260 --> 00:09:59,490
Is Brother Shao Tian in?

129
00:09:59,490 --> 00:10:02,450
Miss Wu. Let's go in and talk.

130
00:10:02,450 --> 00:10:04,640
Did Brother Shao Tian already leave?

131
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:06,510
He left about one and a half hour ago.

132
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:11,300
He said that he's going on a business trip and will be back in six months.

133
00:10:11,300 --> 00:10:12,850
No need, Aunt.

134
00:10:12,850 --> 00:10:14,920
Brother Shao Tian really left?

135
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:19,350
Why didn't he tell me?

136
00:10:19,350 --> 00:10:24,010
He did so much for me and I didn't know anything about it.

137
00:10:25,450 --> 00:10:29,190
Miss Wu. Please don't blame him.

138
00:10:29,190 --> 00:10:36,160
He has been working night and day ever since he joined Rong Da just to give you a better life.

139
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:40,480
He didn't tell you about his business trip? It's probably that he's afraid you might worry.

140
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:42,940
I'm not blaming Brother Shao Tian.

141
00:10:42,940 --> 00:10:45,290
I'm only blaming myself.

142
00:10:45,290 --> 00:10:49,000
Brother Shao Tian is the General Manager of Rong Da

143
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:52,130
and you are still living here.

144
00:10:52,130 --> 00:10:55,500
He helped me to buy back my home.

145
00:10:55,500 --> 00:10:57,940
It's my fault.

146
00:10:57,940 --> 00:10:59,830
I misjudged Brother Shao Tian.

147
00:10:59,830 --> 00:11:04,950
Miss Wu, don't be sad over this.

148
00:11:04,950 --> 00:11:09,080
Brother Shao Tian and I are used to living here.

149
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:13,060
He is very sincere about you and thinks on your behalf.

150
00:11:13,060 --> 00:11:16,060
Frankly, I'm very happy.

151
00:11:16,060 --> 00:11:21,380
I was afraid that he would still hold grudges in his heart.

152
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:25,200
Aunt, what do you mean?

153
00:11:26,340 --> 00:11:31,020
I'm saying that I thought he was being good to you because you came from a rich family

154
00:11:31,020 --> 00:11:34,090
but after having gone through this, I understand now.

155
00:11:34,090 --> 00:11:38,910
Shao Tiao really likes you. I'm very happy.

156
00:11:40,370 --> 00:11:44,890
Aunt, I will visit you another day. I'm going to find Brother Shao Tian.

157
00:11:44,890 --> 00:11:47,590
Foolish child. Shao Tian already left one and a half hours ago.

158
00:11:47,590 --> 00:11:49,960
He has already left the city gate. How are you going to find him?

159
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:54,040
Aunt, don't worry. Regardless of where he went, I will look for him.

160
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:19,430
<i>Brother Shao Tian,</i>

161
00:12:19,430 --> 00:12:21,420
<i>sorry.</i>

162
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:23,510
<i>It's my fault.</i>

163
00:12:24,430 --> 00:12:29,780
<i>You treated me so well and I still suspected you.</i>

164
00:12:49,860 --> 00:12:57,900
