165
00:13:08,170 --> 00:13:11,170
Why are you standing alone here?

166
00:13:11,170 --> 00:13:14,430
Are you trying to slack off from work?

167
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:17,350
I made a mistake about Brother Shao Tian.

168
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:22,780
What did he tell you?

169
00:13:22,780 --> 00:13:28,310
Lu Man lent him money. Brother Shao Tian went to Shanghai to give the General clothes.

170
00:13:28,310 --> 00:13:30,090
but

171
00:13:31,010 --> 00:13:37,020
he needs to deliver it through the Jiangsu and Zhejiang blockage. <i>Battlefield</i>

172
00:13:37,710 --> 00:13:39,900
It will be very dangerous.

173
00:13:41,030 --> 00:13:43,190
If Brother Shao Tian

174
00:13:44,970 --> 00:13:47,290
gets into trouble...

175
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:54,980
My... my life will be condemned.

176
00:13:55,970 --> 00:13:57,930
It's my fault.

177
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:02,000
I blamed him by mistake.

178
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:05,940
He has been totally sincere about me.

179
00:14:47,100 --> 00:14:50,060
I heard that you didn't eat anything for the entire night.

180
00:14:50,060 --> 00:14:52,020
Here.

181
00:14:52,020 --> 00:14:54,490
Eat something now.

182
00:14:54,490 --> 00:14:58,960
Thank you. I don't have an appetite.

183
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:07,790
Do you know that your form of self-abuse will cause my family problems?

184
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:16,020
Is he that important to you?

185
00:15:40,330 --> 00:15:44,270
Mr Zhou. We will be able to reach your home in two or three days.

186
00:15:44,270 --> 00:15:47,310
Row faster. It should take us about two days.

187
00:15:47,310 --> 00:15:49,440
Boatman, can you speed up?

188
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:53,700
This is already very fast, Second Master. I'm more anxious than you. This place is very chaotic.

189
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:58,630
Bullets could fly past. If I didn't need to support my family, who would want to come here to do this business?

190
00:15:58,630 --> 00:16:01,550
Look. Do you see any other boats here?

191
00:16:01,550 --> 00:16:08,300
This place is very dangerous. Others wouldn't want to come here but why you?

192
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:13,070
Mr Zhou. I won't hide from you. No one wants to take on such a dangerous task

193
00:16:13,070 --> 00:16:16,670
but I'm not doing this because they paid me double.

194
00:16:16,670 --> 00:16:19,420
My mom is sick and she is waiting for my money to see the doctor.

195
00:16:19,420 --> 00:16:22,950
I wonder if my mom is feeling better.

196
00:16:28,610 --> 00:16:32,130
Take this money. The money that you received in double is not that much.

197
00:16:32,130 --> 00:16:38,410
Use this money to take your mom to the doctor. Don't take on such a dangerous task in the future. Stay home and look after your mom.

198
00:16:38,410 --> 00:16:41,330
Mr Zhou. I can't take this money.

199
00:16:41,330 --> 00:16:43,720
Life is hard for everyone.

200
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:47,660
If it wasn't, you wouldn't be undertaking in this dangerous task either.

201
00:16:47,660 --> 00:16:50,310
Listen to me. Take the money.

202
00:16:50,310 --> 00:16:54,250
I'm also here because of someone very important.

203
00:16:54,250 --> 00:16:56,990
Your parents are still alive. Grasp the opportunity to show filial piety (to them).

204
00:16:56,990 --> 00:17:00,760
Don't regret it when they're gone.

205
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:03,330
You will suffer and regret it.

206
00:17:25,360 --> 00:17:29,620
Wu Cai Hong. What do you want to do?

207
00:17:30,730 --> 00:17:37,730
Brother Shao Tian must be lacking in food by now.

208
00:17:37,730 --> 00:17:41,810
He could also be injured.

209
00:17:43,750 --> 00:17:47,860
Why do you always expect the worst?

210
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:56,070
The day Brother Shao Tian lit up paper latterns,

211
00:17:56,070 --> 00:18:00,780
why didn't I give him a chance to explain?

212
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:08,070
He waited for me the entire night that day.

213
00:18:08,860 --> 00:18:15,030
At that time, was he in the same mood as I am now?

214
00:18:19,950 --> 00:18:21,930
Listen carefully to me.

215
00:18:21,930 --> 00:18:25,830
You are the servant of the Jiang family. I'm ordering you to eat, drink and sleep

216
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:27,900
and do your work properly.

217
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:47,010
Boatman, row faster.

218
00:18:47,010 --> 00:18:48,820
Okay.

219
00:18:48,820 --> 00:18:51,500
Let me take a look. Mr Zhou, you hand is injured.

220
00:18:51,500 --> 00:18:54,340
I'm fine. Boatman, row faster!

221
00:18:54,340 --> 00:18:57,060
- Quick.
- Okay.

222
00:19:09,060 --> 00:19:12,500
Miss. Zhou Shao Tian is back.

223
00:19:13,390 --> 00:19:14,810
Did he complete his task?

224
00:19:14,810 --> 00:19:17,280
Yes.

225
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:20,670
This Zhou Shao Tian didn't disappoint me.

226
00:19:20,670 --> 00:19:27,030
Mr Wu is very satisfied, Miss. He said it went well during a critical time.

227
00:19:30,050 --> 00:19:33,080
Where is Zhou Shao Tian? Why didn't he find me when he' returned?

228
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:34,320
He is injured.

229
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:37,450
Thus, I sent men to take him to the hospital.

230
00:19:37,450 --> 00:19:39,700
Is his injury serious?

231
00:19:39,700 --> 00:19:45,380
This won't do. Uncle Lai, get the rickshaw ready. I'm going to the hospital to see him.

232
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:49,000
Miss. Are you worried about Zhou Shao Tian?

233
00:19:50,010 --> 00:19:52,140
I'm not worried about him.

234
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:55,980
If I retain this person, he will be able to do other tasks for me in the future.

235
00:19:58,530 --> 00:20:03,930
Uncle Lai. Can you find someone to deliver a letter to Wu Cai Hong?

236
00:20:03,930 --> 00:20:06,250
Since Zhou Shao Tian is in this condition,

237
00:20:06,250 --> 00:20:10,340
I think he would want to see Wu Cai Hong very much.

238
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:16,340
He did such a big favour for me. I should be happy on his behalf.

239
00:20:16,340 --> 00:20:18,990
Okay, I will do it immediately.

240
00:20:34,650 --> 00:20:37,550
Shao Tian, how are you feeling?

241
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:40,770
I heard that you were injured and I rushed here.

242
00:20:40,770 --> 00:20:43,780
Doctor, how is his injury?

243
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:46,280
Provide me with the best medicines. Don't cut any costs.

244
00:20:46,280 --> 00:20:50,570
-Alright.
Mr. Zhou's injuries are all exterior but it's a bit deep.

245
00:20:50,570 --> 00:20:52,570
Also, he came a bit late.

246
00:20:52,570 --> 00:20:57,200
But Miss Lu, don't worry. I gave the best medicines to Mr Zhou.

247
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:59,340
Thank you, Doctor.

248
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:03,370
Shao Tian, how are you feeling now? Does it still hurt?

249
00:21:05,100 --> 00:21:08,740
You really helped me with a big task. I didn't misjudge you.

250
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:12,250
Looks like I should thank you well.

251
00:21:12,250 --> 00:21:15,050
I'm going out first. Call me if there is anything.

252
00:21:15,050 --> 00:21:16,480
Have a good rest.

253
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:19,090
- Thank you.
- Thank you, Doctor.

254
00:21:23,740 --> 00:21:29,050
Ms. Lu gave me such a big task. I practically lost my life.

255
00:21:30,730 --> 00:21:36,090
