258
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:50,100
If I died, you would have benefited the most. Rong Da would have belonged to you.

259
00:21:50,100 --> 00:21:53,450
Who do you take me for?

260
00:21:57,240 --> 00:22:00,890
I have no interest in your petty Rong Da.

261
00:22:00,890 --> 00:22:05,080
What I want is Ling Long's secret formula.

262
00:22:08,250 --> 00:22:11,980
Enough. Didn't you come back safely?

263
00:22:11,980 --> 00:22:15,970
Moreover, your efforts were not wasted.

264
00:22:15,970 --> 00:22:19,080
I already sent someone to ask Miss Wu to come here.

265
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:24,090
Your lover was crying as if the world had ended so of course, she will come.

266
00:22:25,020 --> 00:22:27,520
Will Cai Hong really come?

267
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:31,690
She'll definitely come. You can count on it.

268
00:22:31,690 --> 00:22:37,760
Not long after you left, she came to ask me if I really lent you the money.

269
00:22:37,760 --> 00:22:39,720
What did you reply to her?

270
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:42,370
Of course, I said a lot of good things about you.

271
00:22:42,370 --> 00:22:45,430
Talked about your love, even the gods would be shaking.

272
00:22:45,430 --> 00:22:47,890
I have a good gut feeling about Cai Hong.

273
00:22:47,890 --> 00:22:50,160
You don't need to tell me about your gut feelings.

274
00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:53,730
Okay, I talked too much.

275
00:22:53,730 --> 00:22:55,550
But this time,

276
00:22:55,550 --> 00:22:57,650
you really escaped death.

277
00:22:57,650 --> 00:23:02,130
One must not play with fate.

278
00:23:02,130 --> 00:23:04,030
Was it worth it?

279
00:23:05,750 --> 00:23:09,070
It's worth it as long as she's happy.

280
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:15,950
Brother Shao Tian.

281
00:23:19,450 --> 00:23:21,580
Brother Shao Tian.

282
00:23:23,790 --> 00:23:25,650
Miss Lu.

283
00:23:26,560 --> 00:23:31,000
Okay. Seeing that you are alive, I don't have to worry anymore.

284
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:32,580
I'm leaving first,

285
00:23:32,580 --> 00:23:35,870
so as to not disturb you two.

286
00:23:41,030 --> 00:23:42,770
Brother Shao Tian.

287
00:23:42,770 --> 00:23:45,010
What's wrong with your hand?

288
00:23:45,010 --> 00:23:48,660
Is it serious? Why are you in this condition?

289
00:23:48,660 --> 00:23:51,790
You went to the frontline without even telling me.

290
00:23:51,790 --> 00:23:54,270
Did you know that I was worried about you every day?

291
00:23:54,270 --> 00:23:58,080
I was afraid that you would be hurt and wouldn't be able to eat properly. You are still smiling?

292
00:23:58,080 --> 00:24:00,370
Can't you see that I'm fine?

293
00:24:00,370 --> 00:24:03,240
Cai Hong, it's no big deal. Seriously.

294
00:24:03,240 --> 00:24:04,950
Aren't I back now?

295
00:24:05,910 --> 00:24:07,650
Let me ask you.

296
00:24:07,650 --> 00:24:09,960
Do you still blame me?

297
00:24:13,030 --> 00:24:15,120
It's my fault.

298
00:24:15,120 --> 00:24:18,270
I shouldn't have suspected you.

299
00:24:18,270 --> 00:24:22,960
I would like to apologise to you. Will you forgive me?

300
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:25,440
I don't blame you at all.

301
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:30,940
Being able to come back safely and see you, I'm already very happy.

302
00:24:33,530 --> 00:24:35,380
Promise me then.

303
00:24:35,380 --> 00:24:40,060
Promise me that you won't do such foolish things again.

304
00:24:40,060 --> 00:24:45,930
It's not important whether I get back my home or not. I only want you to be safe.

305
00:24:47,050 --> 00:24:48,940
I already lost my father.

306
00:24:48,940 --> 00:24:50,940
I don't want to lose you either.

307
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:57,490
I promise you that I will never ever leave you.

308
00:25:00,770 --> 00:25:03,000
Promise me too, okay?

309
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:05,740
Trust me.

310
00:25:05,740 --> 00:25:07,940
We will forever be together.

311
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:13,070
I promise you.

312
00:25:17,330 --> 00:25:19,080
The doctor told me just now that

313
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:21,330
I can be discharged early.

314
00:25:21,330 --> 00:25:23,370
I will take you home.

315
00:25:24,840 --> 00:25:26,140
You can really be discharged?

316
00:25:26,140 --> 00:25:27,570
Of course, I can.

317
00:25:27,570 --> 00:25:32,340
Think about it. My mom hasn't seen me for a long time. She must have missed me like crazy.

318
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:36,900
Moreover, if she sees me taking you home, she will be extremely happy.

319
00:25:44,830 --> 00:25:47,270
I'm back.

320
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:49,350
Shao Tian is back?

321
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:52,690
Miss Wu is also here?

322
00:25:52,690 --> 00:25:55,230
Shao Tian, what's wrong with you?

323
00:25:55,230 --> 00:25:58,340
- It's nothing major.
- Why are you injured?

324
00:25:58,340 --> 00:26:01,400
Aren't I back safe and sound? Don't kick up a big fuss.

325
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:04,790
No. How could you be injured on a business trip?

326
00:26:04,790 --> 00:26:06,790
Did you fight with someone?

327
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:12,790
I helped Rong Da send the General cloth. While traveling through the blockade, we were shot at.

328
00:26:12,790 --> 00:26:17,450
Are you crazy? You want money instead of your life? It was such a dangerous task and you still dared to do it.

329
00:26:17,450 --> 00:26:20,130
Aunt, please don't blame Brother Shao Tian.

330
00:26:20,130 --> 00:26:23,310
He did this for me,

331
00:26:23,310 --> 00:26:27,670
but he already promised me that he will never leave me again.

332
00:26:27,670 --> 00:26:30,950
He also swore that he wouldn't do any more dangerous tasks in the future.

333
00:26:30,950 --> 00:26:33,120
I already swore to Cai Hong that

334
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:35,760
I won't do any dangerous tasks again in the future.

335
00:26:35,760 --> 00:26:39,180
But I did it for money this time.

336
00:26:39,180 --> 00:26:43,970
It's so that you will have a daughter-in-law and grandchildren soon.

337
00:26:46,740 --> 00:26:48,780
Really?

338
00:26:48,780 --> 00:26:52,760
But my words don't count. Cai Hong still needs to nod her head.

339
00:26:54,280 --> 00:27:00,470
Miss Wu. Will you nod your head or not?

340
00:27:06,930 --> 00:27:09,330
Excellent.

341
00:27:09,330 --> 00:27:11,720
I have been waiting for this day.

342
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:14,580
Stay here for a meal. I'm going to prepare it now.

343
00:27:14,580 --> 00:27:16,940
Let's go in.

344
00:27:31,260 --> 00:27:32,910
You don't need to see me off.

345
00:27:32,910 --> 00:27:36,190
You are still injured. Stay home and have a good rest.

346
00:27:37,820 --> 00:27:43,720
Look, my wrist's injury is not that bad.
Let me take you home.

347
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:46,940
Brother Shao, don't worry.

348
00:27:46,940 --> 00:27:50,520
I will come again if I have the time.

349
00:27:50,520 --> 00:27:53,860
Okay, be careful on the way home.

350
00:28:13,540 --> 00:28:18,690
Shao Tian. I can tell that Miss Wu is a good girl.

351
00:28:18,690 --> 00:28:22,520
There are certain things that can't be bought in the world.

352
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:24,990
You must treasure her.

353
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:08,340
Sorry for coming back late.

354
00:29:13,980 --> 00:29:16,180
Is Zhou Shao Tian back?

355
00:29:18,380 --> 00:29:21,860
He went to the frontline to deliver cloth?

356
00:29:25,050 --> 00:29:30,700
He did this to buy back my home. He almost lost his life.

357
00:29:31,330 --> 00:29:34,090
I made a mistake about him.

358
00:29:36,550 --> 00:29:39,330
Looks like his plan really worked.

359
00:29:39,330 --> 00:29:41,890
You are not allowed to say that about Brother Shao Tian.

360
00:29:41,890 --> 00:29:45,240
Also, stay out of my business.

361
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:50,020
I don't want anyone to ruin our relationship.

362
00:29:50,020 --> 00:29:53,320
I really want to find out the truth.

363
00:29:53,320 --> 00:29:58,180
I swear that I will not suspect Brother Shao Tian again.

364
00:29:58,180 --> 00:30:00,790
I will believe every single word that he says.

365
00:30:14,360 --> 00:30:17,050
I already told you not to get involved.

366
00:30:17,050 --> 00:30:20,740
So what? Nothing comes out of doing good deeds, right?

