00:30:50,580 --> 00:30:55,080
<i>I don't want anyone to ruin our relationship.</i>

370
00:31:04,910 --> 00:31:06,860
Brother.

371
00:31:06,860 --> 00:31:09,710
What were you thinking about that caused you to look so captivated?

372
00:31:11,310 --> 00:31:13,470
What's wrong?

373
00:31:13,470 --> 00:31:15,740
This is for you.

374
00:31:15,740 --> 00:31:19,070
It seems to be a telegram from overseas.

375
00:31:19,070 --> 00:31:24,030
<i>Dear Mr Zhou Shao Tian, the Parker pen that you bought from us on April 1923</i>

376
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:27,310
<i>is a luxurious item so it's under a lifetime guarantee.</i>

377
00:31:27,310 --> 00:31:33,040
<i>If there are any issues, you can send the item back.</i>

378
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:37,410
Brother. Isn't this telegram for Zhou Shao Tian?

379
00:31:37,410 --> 00:31:42,970
Why is it addressed to you at this place?

380
00:31:50,790 --> 00:31:53,260
Where are you going?

381
00:31:53,260 --> 00:31:56,800
I'm going to find Brother Shao Tian. I already completed my tasks for today.

382
00:31:56,800 --> 00:31:59,980
- Moreover, I already...
- Fine, I will go with you to see him.

383
00:32:04,570 --> 00:32:10,930
Even though I'm your maid, regarding the matters between Brother Shao Tian and I, you can't get involved.

384
00:32:14,750 --> 00:32:17,720
Wait until you read this

385
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:20,380
and see if you still believe Brother Shao Tian.

386
00:32:20,380 --> 00:32:22,340
But I won't look at it.

387
00:32:22,340 --> 00:32:27,350
No matter what you say, I will always trust Brother Shao Tian.

388
00:32:27,350 --> 00:32:31,160
He has another Parker pen from America after your father passed away.

389
00:32:59,110 --> 00:33:01,470
Read it.

390
00:33:08,310 --> 00:33:10,330
<i>Leave this task to me.</i>

391
00:33:10,330 --> 00:33:14,320
<i>I will order the same pen for your father's birthday.</i>

392
00:33:14,320 --> 00:33:16,810
<i>It's a Parker pen.</i>

393
00:33:19,330 --> 00:33:21,520
Impossible.

394
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:24,160
Brother Shao Tian would never do this.

395
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:26,420
I'm going to ask him.

396
00:33:30,980 --> 00:33:33,070
Coming.

397
00:33:37,080 --> 00:33:39,080
Miss Wu.

398
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:40,760
- Aunt.
- Young Master Shao?

399
00:33:40,760 --> 00:33:44,040
- Aunt.
- Why are the both of you together?

400
00:33:44,040 --> 00:33:46,280
Is Brother Shao Tian in?

401
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:48,720
Please come in and talk about this.

402
00:33:48,720 --> 00:33:52,970
It's like this. I have something important to ask Brother Shao Tian.

403
00:33:52,970 --> 00:33:54,610
Shao Tian went out.

404
00:33:54,610 --> 00:34:01,380
He has been nursing his injuries for half a month. If you didn't visit him often, he would have gone back to work.

405
00:34:01,380 --> 00:34:06,850
He came back to say that he's leaving on a business trip and won't be back today.

406
00:34:06,850 --> 00:34:08,840
Aunt.

407
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:13,260
I would like to know if Brother Shao Tian owns a Parker Pen.

408
00:34:13,260 --> 00:34:15,190
Parker pen?

409
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:18,380
Yes.

410
00:34:18,380 --> 00:34:23,020
It's exactly the same as this.

411
00:34:26,980 --> 00:34:31,840
It seems so. Yes, I saw him bringing out a fountain pen.

412
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:33,420
He was very careful about it.

413
00:34:33,420 --> 00:34:35,720
He ordered it from overseas.

414
00:34:35,720 --> 00:34:37,340
Do you know roughly when?

415
00:34:37,340 --> 00:34:38,990
Yes.

416
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:44,420
It was on the day when the incident happened to Old Master Wu.

417
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:46,640
I'm old.

418
00:34:46,640 --> 00:34:49,390
I can't remember things

419
00:34:49,390 --> 00:34:52,380
but it just so happens that it was on the day of your father's incident.

420
00:34:52,380 --> 00:34:54,820
Thus, I could still remember it.

421
00:34:57,210 --> 00:35:03,350
How could that be? Why would Brother Shao Tian own the same pen?

422
00:35:03,350 --> 00:35:05,710
I'm going to ask him.

423
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:07,330
Miss Wu.

424
00:35:07,330 --> 00:35:09,540
Young Master Jiang, what's going on?

425
00:35:09,540 --> 00:35:11,940
What's wrong with Shao Tian?

426
00:35:12,730 --> 00:35:16,990
Aunt. Regarding this, it's better that you ask him yourself.

427
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:09,120
When I was fifteen years old,

428
00:36:10,480 --> 00:36:15,370
when my mother had a stroke, I was reading a book.

429
00:36:16,570 --> 00:36:20,880
Even when her temperament wasn't good,

430
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:23,830
I would take care of her diligently every day.

431
00:36:24,760 --> 00:36:30,950
I was afraid that every single word and action would make her angry.

432
00:36:32,770 --> 00:36:36,450
No matter what, I would tread carefully around her

433
00:36:36,450 --> 00:36:39,550
but she was still afraid that she would exhaust me.

434
00:36:39,550 --> 00:36:42,060
She left me.

435
00:36:49,720 --> 00:36:54,960
It wasn't easy for me to accept my mom's death.

436
00:36:56,410 --> 00:37:01,870
Now, I need to face my father's death.

437
00:37:03,810 --> 00:37:07,100
I don't know who harmed my father.

438
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:11,420
During that short period of time,

439
00:37:11,420 --> 00:37:14,590
Brother Shao Tian was with me.

440
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:17,150
He comforted me.

441
00:37:17,150 --> 00:37:22,420
I thought that I would be able to rely on him forever

442
00:37:25,040 --> 00:37:29,490
but now, I suspect that Brother Shao Tian

443
00:37:29,490 --> 00:37:32,150
is my father's killer.

444
00:37:33,930 --> 00:37:37,390
I don't know why he did that.

445
00:37:44,580 --> 00:37:48,560
There are certain things that will sound cruel when I speak about it, but I still think

446
00:37:48,560 --> 00:37:54,030
you need to know. In fact, you should think seriously about it.

447
00:37:55,370 --> 00:37:59,640
Do you really think that Zhou Shao Tian's life is worth that much money?

448
00:37:59,640 --> 00:38:04,540
Was it really worth Miss Lu paying such a high price just to tell him to complete a mission?

449
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:07,220
Don't you find it very strange?

450
00:38:08,420 --> 00:38:13,650
But if his money is from Ling Long,

451
00:38:13,650 --> 00:38:17,350
it becomes a different matter of course.

452
00:38:17,350 --> 00:38:19,820
You are too cruel!

453
00:38:21,130 --> 00:38:25,350
Why do you want me to believe that the only person who I trust is the killer of my father?

454
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:31,540
I don't believe it.

455
00:38:34,710 --> 00:38:37,580
I don't believe it.

456
00:38:44,690 --> 00:38:47,190
Come in.

457
00:38:47,190 --> 00:38:49,110
Director Chen Suo.

458
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:54,810
This is the reply from the overseas office of the Parker pen.

459
00:38:54,810 --> 00:38:56,780
It clearly proves that

460
00:38:56,780 --> 00:39:02,690
prior to Wu Hong's death, Zhou Shao Tian purchased a Parker pen and it

461
00:39:02,690 --> 00:39:04,710
is exactly the same as mine.

462
00:39:04,710 --> 00:39:10,320
This telegram contains really important information and it's compelling evidence.

463
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:16,560
Shi Jie. Since there is new evidence, do your best to break this case.

464
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:20,320
Give Mr Jiang and Miss Wu an explanation as soon as possible.

465
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,720
Yes.

466
00:39:23,020 --> 00:39:28,360
Mr Jiang, Miss Wu, Director Chen will take care of the matter.

467
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:31,290
Don't be too anxious,

468
00:39:31,290 --> 00:39:35,540
but Wu Hong Da's case was a long time ago.

469
00:39:35,540 --> 00:39:40,570
The longer the timeframe, the higher possibility that someone tampered with the evidence.

470
00:39:40,570 --> 00:39:43,940
To add further, his injury wasn't from a fountain pen.

471
00:39:43,940 --> 00:39:47,940
A fountain pen doesn't prove that he committed a crime.

472
00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:55,480
Miss Wu, me saying this is not me pushing the blame

473
00:39:55,480 --> 00:40:00,640
on the relationship between you and Zhou Shao Tian. I will not give you the reason of the law to fight.

474
00:40:00,640 --> 00:40:06,330
But don't you worry, the police will not let go of anyone. If it's really Zhou Shao Tian's doing,

475
00:40:06,330 --> 00:40:08,980
he will be dealt with accordingly.

476
00:40:08,980 --> 00:40:11,060
Okay, we know.

477
00:40:11,950 --> 00:40:13,330
<i>Shi Jie.
- Superintendent Ting.</i>

478
00:40:13,330 --> 00:40:15,980
I will let you be responsible for this case.

479
00:40:15,980 --> 00:40:20,460
If you face any difficulties, report to me and I will give you my utmost support.

480
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:23,900
I hope that you can break the case soon and give them an explanation.

481
00:40:23,900 --> 00:40:25,270
Yes.

482
00:40:26,140 --> 00:40:27,900
Cai Hong, don't worry.

483
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:32,020
I will definitely give your father in heaven an explanation.

